OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDJs pay emotional tributes 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto 'radio legend'          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tributes have poured in for Steve      
OL,6, Wright, with fellow DJs remembering him
OL,7, as a broadcasting "legend" and a "radio
OL,8, genius".                               
OL,10,FNicki Chapman, who is filling in for   
OL,11,FZoe Ball on Radio 2's breakfast show   
OL,12,Fthis week, was moved to tears on air.  
OL,14,F"I said to myself I wasn't going to cry
OL,15,Fand I have done it once," she said as  
OL,16,Fshe read out messages from listeners.  
OL,18,FWright, who hosted shows on BBC Radio 1
OL,19,Fand Radio 2 for more than four decades,
OL,20,Fdied on Tuesday at the age of 69.      
